parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or lose motive power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shudders
jerks
or hesitates when shifting gears
the transmission warning light is illuminated
the vehicle fails to respond when the accelerator pedal is depressed
the vehicle stalls or loses power
and the transmission makes abnormal sounds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause the vehicle to shudder, jerk, or hesitate when shifting gears, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
and the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TCM can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission warning light is illuminated
the vehicle fails to respond when the accelerator pedal is depressed
the vehicle stalls or loses power
and the transmission makes abnormal sounds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electric power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult or impossible to turn, leading to loss of control of the vehicle, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Intermittent or permanent loss of power steering assist
steering wheel becomes difficult or impossible to turn
steering wheel locks up
warning lights or messages appear on the dashboard
grinding or noise when turning the steering wheel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering rack and pinion can cause the steering wheel to become difficult or impossible to turn, leading to loss of control of the vehicle, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Grinding or noise when turning the steering wheel
steering wheel becomes difficult or impossible to turn
steering wheel locks up
warning lights or messages appear on the dashboard.
